{"tid":420450,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解踩單車高波一陣就覺得肌肉酸 但跑步跑10km都唔會有","createTime":"2017-10-01T11:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T00:44:32.000Z","uid":66686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"92dfb623b24b97d7c6e83fb96ab0f5fb36ae2c62","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T11:54:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6680798e6b582e26e57d4269597165917be05460","tid":420450,"uid":35463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:23:23.000Z","msg":"高強度vs底強度<br />\n<br />\n同埋跑步用嘅肌肉由細用到大"},{"pid":"e91501850a9719d49e98f1967f629a8299d99f46","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高強度vs底強度<br />\n<br />\n同埋跑步用嘅肌肉由細用到大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用嘅肌肉唔同？<br />\n但動作差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8eb9c3ca27b41753eee4946c415047f4751661","tid":420450,"uid":30058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:48:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高強度vs底強度<br />\n<br />\n同埋跑步用嘅肌肉由細用到大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用嘅肌肉唔同？<br />\n但動作差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n發力動作都唔同<br />\n更何況高波果個對抗力高咁多<br />\n一係就負重跑步"},{"pid":"8e201cbcf1d1ae7abd2e3b4466e3ecb513cebbd1","tid":420450,"uid":35087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"因為你廢"},{"pid":"720a654602523e6d067b48b4009013994cf06c00","tid":420450,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T03:53:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>高強度vs底強度<br />\n<br />\n同埋跑步用嘅肌肉由細用到大</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用嘅肌肉唔同？<br />\n但動作差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係專家答唔到你係咪同一組肌肉，但我自己覺得兩種運動用唔同肌肉喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有你高波爆就好似跑一百米咁，接近無氧運動的話，乳酸積累，自然會覺得酸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d436b0e939c4f222d1b059ef6cd1c2d18236b4f","tid":420450,"uid":107571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:17:10.000Z","msg":"因為發力大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n即係舉啞鈴同舉高隻手分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87befba0169c2a17cdd4f6a15f654ed541e2484d","tid":420450,"uid":83819,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:20:08.000Z","msg":"騎車同跑步用既肌肉群組唔同"},{"pid":"2b9046aba194efac4c4da101590d7a09e25e0c3b","tid":420450,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T04:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主冇讀物理<br />\n單車快過跑步n陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動能都多過跑步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7467072fccfbed35190173700714465d12f7671a","tid":420450,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:01:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主冇讀物理<br />\n單車快過跑步n陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動能都多過跑步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d255ede1830faa35aa11ef5c3a33134c5c500d20","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主冇讀物理<br />\n單車快過跑步n陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動能都多過跑步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n跑步有能量用用升起個人<br />\n單車無"},{"pid":"9163beb74e60ade8f8063dc0e2ea298856d5a4b8","tid":420450,"uid":35463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T05:08:06.000Z","msg":"好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步"},{"pid":"deaf4be7f2de180e9f6c1fe2a44ca239bcf17385","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fde8d44332a558c4eafb2f0c8e237aef58ac1e1","tid":420450,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T13:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n😂😂😂😂😂😂唔怪知啦<br />\n踩街同踩機2回事黎，踩機其實極痛苦，因為要不停轉=踩街全程遇逆風、同上山<br />\n單車d精英訓練，好多時都係踩機為主，因為最易控制心跳同最少意外<br />\n踩街唔同，食下順風、落斜就輕輕鬆鬆"},{"pid":"c05593b95f1842736c704f42887572a8603d4fcc","tid":420450,"uid":35463,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T14:42:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n較返啱個位置，姿勢<br />\n睇住power嚟踩<br />\n開頭低watt高腳頻<br />\n慢慢先踩高強度<br />\n盡量keep耐啲"},{"pid":"0a3721e2f1198a19fb5dc03b93fb38164e73b5cb","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:28:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n較返啱個位置，姿勢<br />\n睇住power嚟踩<br />\n開頭低watt高腳頻<br />\n慢慢先踩高強度<br />\n盡量keep耐啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁踩幾多watt好<br />\n想減肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50fe793adf561a9dd93296a29d5b38e115ae6ca4","tid":420450,"uid":61325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主冇讀物理<br />\n單車快過跑步n陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動能都多過跑步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n物理學生物學天材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8c8f22cfcbd1856b38c1de8be11c19e295f2c6","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n😂😂😂😂😂😂唔怪知啦<br />\n踩街同踩機2回事黎，踩機其實極痛苦，因為要不停轉=踩街全程遇逆風、同上山<br />\n單車d精英訓練，好多時都係踩機為主，因為最易控制心跳同<span style=\"color: red;\">最少意外</span><br />\n踩街唔同，食下順風、落斜就輕輕鬆鬆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機都可以有意外？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f567c94aaa2f3f8c9e6c2f15c92028a3118590","tid":420450,"uid":36100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n較返啱個位置，姿勢<br />\n睇住power嚟踩<br />\n開頭低watt高腳頻<br />\n慢慢先踩高強度<br />\n盡量keep耐啲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁踩幾多watt好<br />\n想減肚腩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好盲目踩高強度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\ncadence最好keep 90 rpm<br />\n用強度去調校至target heart rate<br />\n高強度好傷膝"},{"pid":"4485523a1d1b8d7051a9877aa0b8648c7d3ce469","tid":420450,"uid":94457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T14:44:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n😂😂😂😂😂😂唔怪知啦<br />\n踩街同踩機2回事黎，踩機其實極痛苦，因為要不停轉=踩街全程遇逆風、同上山<br />\n單車d精英訓練，好多時都係踩機為主，因為最易控制心跳同<span style=\"color: red;\">最少意外</span><br />\n踩街唔同，食下順風、落斜就輕輕鬆鬆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機都可以有意外？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全速爆 一脫腳係有機會拉傷<br />\n雖然機會好微"},{"pid":"75c944475f87e98f8dc04d1598095e53a7a0081b","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好奇一問，巴打踩咩車？<br />\n<br />\nTT/三鐵車用嘅肌肉會較接近跑步</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n😂😂😂😂😂😂唔怪知啦<br />\n踩街同踩機2回事黎，踩機其實極痛苦，因為要不停轉=踩街全程遇逆風、同上山<br />\n單車d精英訓練，好多時都係踩機為主，因為最易控制心跳同<span style=\"color: red;\">最少意外</span><br />\n踩街唔同，食下順風、落斜就輕輕鬆鬆</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n單車機都可以有意外？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全速爆 一脫腳係有機會拉傷<br />\n雖然機會好微</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係有條帶扣住腳同腳踏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果咁都甩就係爆得好快"},{"pid":"356517b9b8a05cc31cc304839712f1b4d2ccff3f","tid":420450,"uid":4703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T15:48:35.000Z","msg":"我當你所指嘅踩單車一陣係三兩分鐘去計<br />\n運動開始嘅頭0-20秒左右身體最主要係用緊無氧系統去供能（分解磷酸肌酸 PC）<br />\n而20秒過後無氧系統開始衰歇<br />\n同時，另一組供能系統就開始接上手力（乳酸系統）<br />\n依一組系統有個特點 就係佢喺用緊身體儲存嘅能量（e.g. 醣）嘅時候會產生一種副產品which is就係乳酸<br />\n過多乳酸積聚喺你肌肉入面嘅時候就會令你感到疲勞<br />\n所以依個就係點解你會覺得踩單車高波一陣會酸同攰嘅最主要原因<br />\n而跑10km係用緊有氧系統 而乳酸係會透過不停運動由血液從肌肉中慢慢帶走<br />\n所以低強度嘅跑步唔覺攰係正常"},{"pid":"1d174cc504223fd537df1735a6084e42eb7ea938","tid":420450,"uid":32536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 樓主冇讀物理<br />\n單車快過跑步n陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n動能都多過跑步啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n物理學生物學天材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔怪得的士佬咁惡 真係唔講得笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36f1a063d1aa0acab92b4290d0a97ab704123230","tid":420450,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我當你所指嘅踩單車一陣係三兩分鐘去計<br />\n運動開始嘅頭0-20秒左右身體最主要係用緊無氧系統去供能（分解磷酸肌酸 PC）<br />\n而20秒過後無氧系統開始衰歇<br />\n同時，另一組供能系統就開始接上手力（乳酸系統）<br />\n依一組系統有個特點 就係佢喺用緊身體儲存嘅能量（e.g. 醣）嘅時候會產生一種副產品which is就係乳酸<br />\n過多乳酸積聚喺你肌肉入面嘅時候就會令你感到疲勞<br />\n所以依個就係點解你會覺得踩單車高波一陣會酸同攰嘅最主要原因<br />\n而跑10km係用緊有氧系統 而乳酸係會透過不停運動由血液從肌肉中慢慢帶走<br />\n所以低強度嘅跑步唔覺攰係正常</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁仲應唔應該繼續好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n算唔算係身體俾出訊號叫停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9e99cd70eeb6943734b4d08b26282a87f392ba5","tid":420450,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T16:21:53.000Z","msg":"你試下2分鐘跑800米睇下酸唔酸，on9你阿婆咁慢跑實無feel架"}]}